ssets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你諗住係邊度開，如果係多唐人嘅地方可以target唐人嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ngold coast 點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我住係gc 你過黎睇下環境先喇<br />\n呢到華人唔算多<br />\n甜品個啲鬼佬未必好<br />\n所以你market好有限制<br />\n加埋12月中會開八號胡同<br />\n一下間開多左好多亞洲野<br />\n唔知有無甜品鋪喇<br />\n但我認識嘅香港人都好想係呢到食到香港甜品<br />\n唔洗走到sunnybank咁遠"},{"pid":"498d4da21ce47d3772b83d568a63f25df168e79a","tid":474210,"uid":124507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T23:01:50.000Z","msg":"GC 我覺得而家開bubble t 有得做下，因為好似唔覺有"},{"pid":"912b8fb130a2ca818504f31f3ea6dd19520d2307","tid":474210,"uid":125218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:52:25.000Z","msg":"琴晚同佢傾完 應該係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實佢係諗住係個到開燒味舖 再加啲小食賣 小籠包燒賣魚蛋etc<br />\n然後橫惦我啱啱quit左份工 可以試下學多樣技能 <br />\n如果真係要公司擔保我過去都可以去見下工咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}